{"tid":2104320,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"康文署職員員確診","createTime":"2020-07-12T00:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T00:52:49.000Z","uid":114217,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"32a1b02d6c5c278d8206bb899116d49cad21c546","tid":2104320,"uid":114217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T00:44:11.000Z","msg":"通州街公園壁球中心及網球場暫時關閉<br />\n****************************************<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　康樂及文化事務署發言人今日（七月十二日）宣布，一名於深水埗區通州街公園壁球中心工作的員工確診感染2019冠狀病毒病，基於公共衞生考慮，通州街公園壁球中心及鄰近之網球場即時關閉，以安排徹底清潔和消毒，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n　　受影響的設施包括壁球室／乒乓球室／多用途活動室、壁球室／乒乓球室、多用途活動室、「康體通」櫃枱服務、更衣室及洗手間，以及網球場。其間，市民可使用同區的其他同類設施。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n2020年7月12日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間6時00分"},{"pid":"42ada305522057d6beb1cfdfb0738b2fbb36084a","tid":2104320,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T00:45:01.000Z","msg":"大爆發<br />\n<br />\n信政府<br />\n唔怕"},{"pid":"e884c8e945133f7ccdcae5616ad190c8f35b99fe","tid":2104320,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T00:45:35.000Z","msg":"抵啦 封足球場呀拿 快啲死全家"},{"pid":"d1f8093e500ea0abd01712addcded6bc5378ab8d","tid":2104320,"uid":104668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T00:45:40.000Z","msg":"公務員如常上班"},{"pid":"1f77018a07843b6a7e2de1e7509cb1385d42ce6a","tid":2104320,"uid":114217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T00:46:24.000Z","msg":"補link: <a href=\"https://www.lcsd.gov.hk/clpss/tc/webApp/NewsDetails.do?id=14941\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lcsd.gov.hk%2Fclpss%2Ftc%2FwebApp%2FNewsDetails.do%3Fid%3D14941&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=f5ca0a49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.lcsd.gov.hk/clpss/tc/webApp/NewsDetails.do?id=14941</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Srgo144.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSrgo144.jpg&h=bef15177&s={SIZE}\" />"